title: Grateful Dead Live at Onongada County War Memorial on 1978-05-09
description:
Set 1

Franklin's Tower, Minglewood Blues, Row Jimmy, Looks Like Rain, Friend Of The Devil, El Paso, Candyman, Passenger, Deal

Set 2

Samson & Delilah, Ship of Fools, Dancin' In The Streets-> Drums-> Not Fade Away-> Black Peter-> Around & Around, E: Werewolves of London
